entry.title: Hydrologic Outlook issued May 24 at 3:17PM MDT by NWS
entry.summary: ...Expect Increased Flows on the Green River Below Flaming Gorge Reservoir Due to Releases... Releases from Flaming Gorge Reservoir will start to increase tomorrow May 24 and reach around 8600 cfs by the morning of May 26. The release is scheduled to last for 7 days before starting to ramp down.
